FBIS4-62805 "drsov095_b_94024" FBIS-SOV-94-095 Daily Report 14 May 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Economic Issues All Enterprises in Key Timber Area Begin Long Strike All Enterprises in Key Timber Area Begin Long Strike LD1405051594 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 0503 GMT 14 May 94 LD1405051594 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [By ITAR-TASS correspondent Yuriy Grachev] [Text] Chuguyevka, Maritime Territory May 14 -- All industrial enterprises in the maritime territory's main timber-producing areas --Chuguyevka--went on a warning strike from Saturday morning until May 25. The main demand of the strikers is that they be paid overdue wages for several months.
